init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I never told anyone about my fear of bees, and I never let it show.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I always told her that I would be fine, but deep down I was terrified.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I always wore long sleeves and pants, even in the summer, in order to avoid any stings.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My junior year of college, I decided to take a summer job in the city.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was sitting on a lounge chair by the pool when I felt a bee land on my shoulder.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked around and saw that no one else was in the room, so I decided to ask the bee a question.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yes, I am your Majesty's personal bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee told me that I did not have a deadly allergy, and that my mother had lied to me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee told me that my mother had lied to me because she was a bee queen, and she wanted to protect me from her enemies.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I had never heard of wasps, so I asked the bee what they were.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee told me that I was the queen bee, and that I was the only one who could end the war between bees and wasps.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee told me that the first order of business was to find the wasps' queen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I told the bee that I would go to Europe to find the wasp queen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I found the wasp queen's home in a small town in Germany.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She told me that she had known about my plan to come to Europe to find the wasp queen, and she had come to stop me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: My mother told me that the war had been going on for so long, that it was pointless to stop it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The old woman said that she was the wasp queen, and I told her that I was the princess bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We sat at her table and she told me that she had been waiting for me to come and stop the war.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I told her that I agreed with her, and that I wanted to make things right.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was so happy to have ended the war that I hugged my mother and the wasp queen.
